    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/ba3026fec29875c6fc7a1d5e33dc8f14.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Discover a blend of <strong>Strategy</strong>, <strong>Deckbuilding</strong>, and <strong>Roguelite</strong>!<br><strong>Collect</strong> cards, <strong>summon</strong> creatures, <strong>cast</strong> devastating spells, <strong>discover</strong> ancient relics, new realms, and much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/45e6267a67bdb70cc69e62f9f87e11e3.poster.avif?t=1707160786\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/45e6267a67bdb70cc69e62f9f87e11e3.webm?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/45e6267a67bdb70cc69e62f9f87e11e3.mp4?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/98be1fbda79dd5ccded7c7f0f53d8ccd.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><strong>Explore</strong> an <strong>infinite</strong> amount of <strong>realms</strong> to uncover their secrets through the unique vestige system. <strong>Encounter</strong> famed characters and relics of the past that can improve your army or <strong>devastate</strong> the enemy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/b8f10cc5c4abfe66369d50259547ff8a.poster.avif?t=1707160786\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/b8f10cc5c4abfe66369d50259547ff8a.webm?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/b8f10cc5c4abfe66369d50259547ff8a.mp4?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/788c0a03a116d313e1d434498d2aac3d.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Deckbuilding in Infinite Realms melds <strong>strategic depth</strong> with <strong>build customization</strong>. Add new cards to your hero’s deck throughout the game to discover amazing combinations! <br>With a large shared card pool between all heroes, each adventure offers boundless possibilities for ingenious combinations!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/48d13b15458c00ad58ff9bb1fd24aeb5.poster.avif?t=1707160786\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/48d13b15458c00ad58ff9bb1fd24aeb5.webm?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/48d13b15458c00ad58ff9bb1fd24aeb5.mp4?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/23c9683093852181789ae93910dde713.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Enjoy a <strong>dynamic, ever-evolving experience</strong> in a <strong>breathtaking</strong>, fantasy universe. Confront <strong>escalating challenges</strong>, and make each choice count when picking your rewards. Each run is <strong>unique</strong>, demanding flexibility in strategy as you face new trials.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/a6116502a9089c4346a214d3b5a39f71.poster.avif?t=1707160786\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/a6116502a9089c4346a214d3b5a39f71.webm?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/a6116502a9089c4346a214d3b5a39f71.mp4?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/e186e77c949267ef02a4d50662d2f19c.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Each realm unveils a fresh new landscape teeming with resources and new challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/d5782bd132ee9701815b3de1c660d722.poster.avif?t=1707160786\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/d5782bd132ee9701815b3de1c660d722.webm?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/d5782bd132ee9701815b3de1c660d722.mp4?t=1707160786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164160/extras/9a282b4d0e02126ad816494518686998.webp?t=1707160786\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Infinite Realms is an <strong>endless</strong> challenge, with victory an ephemeral glory and defeat lurking behind every corner. Your journey ends when your hero meets their demise or when Morrigan’s corruption swallows the realm. Each decision is critical in prolonging your life in the realm.",
